trans-unit.source: Establishes a relationship between an item stored in an ASP.NET application's <xref href="System.Web.Caching.Cache"></xref> object and either a specific SQL Server database table or the results of a [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] query.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en relasjon mellom et element som er lagret i en ASP.NET-programmet <xref href="System.Web.Caching.Cache"> </xref> objektet enten en bestemt SQL Server-databasen tabell eller resultatet av en [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] spørringen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: On all supported versions of SQL Server (Microsoft SQL Server 7.0, Microsoft SQL Server 2000, and SQL Server 2005) the SqlCacheDependency class monitors a specific SQL Server database table.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SqlCacheDependency overvåker en bestemt tabell for SQL Server-database på alle støttede versjoner av SQL Server (Microsoft SQL Server 7.0, Microsoft SQL Server 2000 og SQL Server 2005).

trans-unit.source: When the table changes, items associated with the table are removed from the <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>, and a new version of the item is added to the <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>.
trans-unit.target: Når endringene tabellen knyttet til tabellen fjernes fra den <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>, og en ny versjon av elementet legges til <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>.</xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> </xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>

trans-unit.source: The SqlCacheDependency class also supports integration with the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDependency?displayProperty=fullName> class when using a [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] database.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SqlCacheDependency støtter også integrasjon med den <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDependency?displayProperty=fullName>klasse når du bruker en [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] database.</xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDependency?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The query notification mechanism of [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] detects changes to data that invalidate the results of an SQL query and removes any cached items associated with the SQL query from the <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Spørringen varsling mekanisme for [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] oppdager endringer i dataene som blir resultatene av en SQL-spørring og fjerner eventuelle bufrede elementer som er knyttet til SQL-spørringen fra <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can use the SqlCacheDependency class to add items to your application's <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> that are dependent on either a SQL Server database table or on an SQL query when using [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke SqlCacheDependency klassen å legge til elementer i programmets <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>som er avhengige på en SQL Server databasetabellen eller på en SQL-spørring ved [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)].</xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>

trans-unit.source: You can also use this class with the directive to make an output-cached page or a user control dependent on a SQL Server database table.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også bruke denne klassen med direktivet foreta en output-hurtigbufret side eller en brukerkontroll avhengig av en SQL Server tabell.

trans-unit.source: Finally, you can use the SqlCacheDependency class with the page directive to make an output-cached page dependent on the results of an SQL query when using [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke SqlCacheDependency klassen med direktivet siden lage en output-hurtigbufret side avhengig av resultatene av en SQL-spørring ved [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Query notification using [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] is not supported on the directive for user controls.
trans-unit.target: Spørringen varsling ved å bruke [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] støttes ikke i direktivet for brukerkontroller.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > For this class to work correctly when using table-based notifications, the database and any tables that you want to make dependencies on must have notifications enabled.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For denne klassen skal fungere riktig ved tabellbasert varsler databasen og noen tabeller som du vil gjøre avhengigheter på må ha varsler aktivert.

trans-unit.source: You can enable notifications by calling methods of the <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin> class or by using the command-line tool.
trans-unit.target: Du kan aktivere varsler ved å kalle metoder for den <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin>klasse eller ved å bruke kommandolinjeverktøyet.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin>

trans-unit.source: In addition, the proper configuration settings must be included in the application's Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg må riktig konfigurasjonsinnstillingene inkluderes i programmets Web.config-filen.

trans-unit.source: > > Using a SqlCacheDependency object with [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] query notification does not require any explicit configuration.
trans-unit.target: >> Ved hjelp av et SqlCacheDependency-objekt med [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] spørringen varsling ikke krever konfigurasjon. eksplisitt.

trans-unit.source: Consult the [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] Books Online for information about restrictions on the types of Transact-SQL queries that are allowed when using query notification.
trans-unit.target: Se den [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] Books Online for informasjon om begrensninger på typer Transact-SQL-spørringer som er tillatt når du bruker spørringsvarsler.

trans-unit.target: Eksemplet nedenfor viser en ASP.NET Web.config-filen som aktiverer tabellbasert avhengigheter i en tabell for SQL Server-databasen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"></xref> class, using the supplied <xref href="System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand"></xref> to create a cache-key dependency.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"> </xref> class, ved hjelp av den angitte <xref href="System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand"> </xref> til å opprette en Hurtigbuffernøkkel avhengighet.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is used to create <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> objects that use the query-notification feature of [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] products.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren brukes til å opprette <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>objekter som bruker funksjonen spørringsvarsler i [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] produkter.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: SQL statements that are associated with the `sqlCmd` parameter must include the following: - Fully qualified table names, including the name of the table owner.
trans-unit.target: SQL-setninger som er knyttet til den `sqlCmd` parameteren må inneholde følgende: – fullstendig kvalifiserte tabellnavn, inkludert navnet på eieren av tabellen.

trans-unit.source: For example, to refer to a table named Customersthat is owned by the database owner, the SQL statement must refer to `dbo.customers`.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel for å referere til en tabell med navnet Customersthat eies av databaseeieren, SQL-setningen må referere til `dbo.customers`.

trans-unit.source: - Explicit column names in the Select statement.
trans-unit.target: -Eksplisitt kolonnenavn i Select-setningen.

trans-unit.source: You cannot use the asterisk (*) wildcard character to select all columns from a table.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ikke bruke jokertegnet stjerne (*) til å velge alle kolonner fra en tabell.

trans-unit.source: For example, instead of `select * from dbo.customers`, you must use `select name, address, city, state from dbo.customers`.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel i stedet for `select * from dbo.customers`, må du bruke `select name, address, city, state from dbo.customers`.

trans-unit.source: This constructor cannot be used to associate a <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand> instance with a <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> instance on a page using [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] query notifications with page-level output caching.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren kan ikke brukes til å knytte et <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand>serverforekomsten med en <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>forekomsten på en side med [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] spørring meldinger med sidenivå utdatahurtigbufring.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> </xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand>

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand"> </xref> som brukes til å opprette en <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"> </xref> class, ved hjelp av parameterne til å opprette en Hurtigbuffernøkkel avhengighet.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is used to create <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> objects for SQL Server 7.0 and SQL Server 2000 products.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren brukes til å opprette <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>objekter for SQL Server 7.0 og SQL Server 2000-produkter.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: The database name passed to the `database` parameter must be defined in the application's Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Databasenavnet ble sendt til den `database` parameteren må være definert i programmets Web.config-filen.

trans-unit.source: For example, the following Web.config file defines a database named pubs for <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> change notifications.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel følgende Web.config-filen definerer en database med navnet PUB for <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>endringsforespørsler.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: ``` <configuration> <connectionStrings> <add name="Pubs" connectionString="Data Source=(local); Initial Catalog=pubs; Integrated Security=true"; providerName="System.Data.SqlClient" /> </connectionStrings> <system.web> <caching> <sqlCacheDependency enabled = "true" pollTime = "60000" > <databases> <add name="pubs" connectionStringName="pubs" pollTime="9000000" /> </databases> </sqlCacheDependency> </caching> </system.web> </configuration> ``` Two exceptions are commonly thrown when this constructor is used: <xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException> and <xref:System.Web.Caching.TableNotEnabledForNotificationException>.
trans-unit.target: ``` <configuration> <connectionStrings> <add name="Pubs" connectionString="Data Source=(local); Initial Catalog=pubs; Integrated Security=true"; providerName="System.Data.SqlClient" /> </connectionStrings> <system.web> <caching> <sqlCacheDependency enabled = "true" pollTime = "60000" > <databases> <add name="pubs" connectionStringName="pubs" pollTime="9000000" /> </databases> </sqlCacheDependency> </caching> </system.web> </configuration> ```To unntak er vanligvis et når denne konstruktøren brukes: <xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException>og <xref:System.Web.Caching.TableNotEnabledForNotificationException>.</xref:System.Web.Caching.TableNotEnabledForNotificationException> </xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException> is thrown, you can call the <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin.EnableNotifications%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method in exception-handling code, or use the command-line tool to set up the database for notifications.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException>er registrert, kan du kalle den <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin.EnableNotifications%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden i unntaksbehandling kode, eller Bruk kommandolinjeverktøyet for å angi at databasen for varsler.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin.EnableNotifications%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Web.Caching.TableNotEnabledForNotificationException> is thrown, you can call the <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin.EnableTableForNotifications%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method or use to set up the table for notifications.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.Web.Caching.TableNotEnabledForNotificationException>er registrert, kan du kalle den <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin.EnableTableForNotifications%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden eller bruk til å definere tabellen for varsler.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependencyAdmin.EnableTableForNotifications%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.Caching.TableNotEnabledForNotificationException>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a unique identifier for a <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en unik identifikator for en <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> method returns an identifier used to uniquely track <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> objects associated with an item or application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>metoden returnerer en identifikator som brukes til å spore unikt <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>objekter som er knyttet til et element eller applikasjonen.</xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> </xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier generated when using table-based notifications is partially dependent on the change identifier generated by the database.
trans-unit.target: Den unike identifikatoren som er generert ved tabellbasert varsler er delvis avhengig av endre-identifikatoren som er generert av databasen.

trans-unit.source: When using SQL Server 2005-based query notifications, the unique identifier is `null` because [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] does not support returning unique identifiers for individual query notifications .
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker SQL Server 2005-baserte spørringsvarsler, er den unike identifikatoren `null` fordi [!INCLUDE[sqprsqlong](~/add/includes/sqprsqlong-md.md)] støtter ikke returnerer unike identifikatorer for individuelle spørringsvarsler.

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier for the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"></xref> object, or null if no identifier can be generated.
trans-unit.target: Den unike identifikatoren for den <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"> </xref> objekt, eller null hvis ingen identifikator kan genereres.
